====Usage notes====
This term should be considered [[apocryphal]] of Irish speech and is a [[stereotype]]. While popularly used in the United States when imitating Irish people, or when celebrating one's Irish heritage (e.g. on {{w|St. Patrick's Day}}), latter-day native Hiberno-English speakers would be unlikely to ever use this phrase. See [[Hollywood Irish]].

